               <p>Q. Look at that acceptance the name of Horn, do you know whose hand writing it is - A. It resembles the prisoner's it is like Mr. Sharp's writing I cannot say exactly; I rather thing it is so than otherwise; I have seen him write often; this bill is drawn by Mr. Sharp, and accepted by him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150405-52-person514">
                  THOMAS 
                  BALLAD
