                  </persName>
            . I was clerk to the prisoner two years; I left him a twelvemonth ago; I know his hand writing.</p>
               <p>Q. Look at that acceptance, and tell me whether that is the prisoner's - A. I think it is not, he write a better hand than that.</p>
